node.text:
🔥FIERY ABS WORKOUT! Save & Try This Superset/Ab Building Workout | Swipe➡️& Tag@ A Friend💪@vqfit #motivation 
-
💥Superset: (A+B)
1) Olympic Bar Upper Crunch - 4 x 10-12
2) Side To Side Leg Raises - 4 x  6-8 Each Side (AMRAP)
